Glenport AG

Is part of group of Ukrainian and foreign companies with 15 years experience in international grain trading. Our main activity â€“ trading of agricultural grains and fertilisers, organising and providing logistical services - from the farmer to the final consumer. Glenport covers the whole supply chain from acquisition of agricultural products through warehousing, transportation by river and sea, documentation and financial modelling, up to point of selling.

Our main values are high level trade service, cooperation and integration, covering all processes from the farmer to the final consumer.

Why us?

We fulfill contract terms regardless of any external factors. From grain elevators to loading on the ship in a matter of days.

Exclusively Ukrainian grains

  • Expertise

    15 years in the market

  • Total turnover

    500-700 thousand metric tons per year

  • Main products

    Corn, wheat, barley, rape seeds, sunflower seeds, peas
